data.description: Come home to this well maintained FIVE BEDROOM home located near Langley Air Force Base!  With 1.5 bathrooms and four bedrooms on the main level, there's room for everyone! Not to mention the master suite upstairs with a full bath - giving much needed relaxation and privacy.  Love to entertain? The deck and backyard is just right for family and friends gatherings! Granite kitchen countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a barely used gas fireplace all compliments your new home!  Shed conveys as is.  Come home for the holidays!  Square footage is per tax records.  Sale is contingent upon seller finding a new home.
